{"tid":1448200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港人同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:28:33.000Z","uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3705c3ead087b78383dea7219427087dc196320e","tid":1448200,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=923b2dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=4900c0b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"f5b38eb8a431b3db1c0c3399549a99217c62a913","tid":1448200,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"091856572afad1902c531ea747bc86c26eee30ab","tid":1448200,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e9649e7ee3deb5684cd009a83758589c42822a89","tid":1448200,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:27.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"31683d921a9b1f62f364835cc4f9eb99a40c3325","tid":1448200,"uid":160499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:27:37.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"63199